---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Coastline Spray Foam Solutions">
  <main class="container mx-auto py-20 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About Coastline Spray Foam Solutions</h1>

    <!-- Company Story -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="md:flex md:gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Founded by a team of passionate building science experts, Coastline Spray Foam Solutions was born from a desire to bring superior insulation technology to the Central East Florida Coastline. We saw a need for a reliable, professional insulation company that not only provides high-quality services but also educates homeowners and businesses on the long-term value of spray foam insulation.</p>
          <p>From our humble beginnings, we have grown into a trusted local business, known for our commitment to quality, integrity, and customer satisfaction. We are proud to serve our community, helping our neighbors save money, improve their comfort, and invest in their properties.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Company Story" class="rounded-lg shadow-md">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission and Values -->
    <section class="mb-16 bg-gray-100 py-12 rounded-lg">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-500 mb-6">Our Mission & Values</h2>
        </div>
      <div class="md:flex justify-center md:gap-8">
        <div class="md:w-1/3 text-center px-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
          <p>To provide the highest quality spray foam insulation services that deliver exceptional value, energy efficiency, and comfort to our clients, while maintaining the highest standards of professionalism and integrity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/3 text-center px-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Our Values</h3>
          <ul class="list-none">
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Excellence:</strong> We strive for perfection in every project.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Integrity:</strong> We operate with honesty and transparency.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Customer Focus:</strong> We put our clients' needs first.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-teal-500 mb-10">Why Choose Us?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Certified Professionals</h3>
          <p>Our team is fully trained and certified in the latest spray foam application techniques, ensuring a safe and effective installation every time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Superior Materials</h3>
          <p>We use only premium, eco-friendly spray foam products that are proven to provide superior performance and longevity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Local Expertise</h3>
          <p>As a local business, we understand the specific climate challenges of the Florida coastline and tailor our solutions accordingly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Unmatched ROI</h3>
          <p>Our insulation services are an investment that pays for itself through significant energy savings and increased property value.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
